is going to be associated with it, run

01:03:52.040 --> 01:03:54.150
your code on different machines, then my

01:03:54.160 --> 01:03:55.790
suggestion is

01:03:55.800 --> 01:03:59.230
to simply use the cores on each machine

01:03:59.240 --> 01:04:01.270
to feed data into the GPUs on that

01:04:01.280 --> 01:04:02.230
